    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And they came to-- they came to-- to finish me up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "When I start to holler, in German language, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Don't kill me, don't kill me, and I start-- and I said, don't kill me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "All the soldiers around me, I said, stay [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I holler, don't kill me!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, came a-- a American-- a Jewish fellow, but older, like 50, 55, something like this, a major.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "With tears in his eyes-- and he kissed me my head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And he said, in Yiddish, in broken Yiddish, [SPEAKING YIDDISH], American [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Yid. ?] My daughters are good [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Yid. ?] My mama are good [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Yid. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
